        "description": {
            "value": "<p>The massive stinger of a black scorpion adds significant weight to this <em>+2 greater striking @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Fearsome] mace</em>. On a critical hit, the target is exposed to black scorpion venom.</p><hr /><p><strong>Black Scorpion Venom</strong> (poison)</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[type:fortitude|dc:36]</p>\n<p><strong>Maximum Duration</strong> 6 rounds</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> @Damage[2d12[poison]] damage and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Clumsy]{Clumsy 2} (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> @Damage[3d12[poison]] damage, clumsy 2, and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> @Damage[4d12[poison]] damage, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Clumsy]{Clumsy 4}, and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 2} (1 round).</p><hr /><p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> The initial raw materials must include the intact stinger of a black scorpion.</p>"
